                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/13745.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Carothers</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Aguascalientes</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-11T23:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 11, 1914, 11 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to property in Zacatecas belonging to German Vice Consul at Guanajuato
                    General Villa has ordered investigated and return of property to owners.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carothers</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
